<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rules of Using Anonymous Chat</title>

    <link href="/css/Rules.css" rel="stylesheet" />

</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Rules of Using Anonymous Chat</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our anonymous chat platform! Before you start engaging in conversations, please take a moment to read and understand the rules of conduct. These rules are designed to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for all users.</p>

        <ol>
            <li><span class="rule">Respect Others:</span> Treat all users with kindness, respect, and empathy. Do not engage in harassment, bullying, or discrimination based on race, ethnicity, gender, religion, sexual orientation, or any other characteristic.</li>
            <li><span class="rule">Keep it Civil:</span> Avoid engaging in heated arguments, political debates, or contentious discussions. Our platform is intended for friendly and constructive conversations.</li>
            <li><span class="rule">Protect Your Privacy:</span> Do not share personal information such as your full name, address, phone number, email address, or any other sensitive details. Your privacy and safety are important to us.</li>
            <li><span class="rule">No Inappropriate Content:</span> Do not share or request explicit or inappropriate content, including but not limited to nudity, violence, hate speech, or illegal activities. Keep the conversations clean and suitable for all audiences.</li>
            <li><span class="rule">Report Abuse:</span> If you encounter any user violating these rules or behaving inappropriately, please report them to the platform moderators immediately. Your reports help us maintain a positive and welcoming environment for everyone.</li>
            <li><span class="rule">Use Common Sense:</span> Exercise caution and use your best judgment when interacting with others. If something feels uncomfortable or suspicious, disengage from the conversation and report it.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>By using our anonymous chat platform, you agree to abide by these rules and guidelines. Failure to comply may result in your account being suspended or banned from the platform.</p>

        <p>Thank you for being a responsible and respectful member of our community. Enjoy your conversations and make meaningful connections!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
